<section class="sales_pitch">

  <div class="sales_pitch__text">
    <h1 class="sales_pitch__header">
      trunc8r makes your links shorter than you ever thought possible.
    </h1>

    <p class="sales_pitch__body">
      You do want your links shorter right? If you don't, then why are you here?
      We don't really do anything else. Seriously. That's it. That's all we do.
    <p>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag("people", alt: "trunc8r axe logo", class: "sales_pitch__image")%>
  
</section>

